# Frontend E2E

- Write scenarios that read as user stories and focus on observable outcomes.
- Prefer semantic selectors (`getByRole`, `getByLabelText`) and avoid raw CSS/XPath selectors.
- Keep each test isolated with explicit setup/teardown and deterministic fixtures.
- Rely on Playwright's built-in waiting/assertions instead of manual `waitForTimeout`.
- Reserve Playwright for critical flows; do not duplicate every unit/integration test here.
